		{% endcall %}
        {% call library.container(class="spirit-container--hero-split-screen", padding_top="none", padding_bottom="sm") %}
            <div class="spirit-hero-split-screen__contents">
                <div class="spirit-hero-split-screen__message spirit-hero-message">
                    <h2 class="spirit-hero-message__title spirit-h2">Recognizable</h2>
                    <div class="spirit-long-form-text">
                        <p>A monochromatic color scheme is used to strengthen the connection with JDRF Blue through consistent repetition.  Color recognition is especially important for JDRF because we have few other recognizable brand elements.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <figure class="spirit-hero-split-screen__image-container spirit-hero-split-screen__image-container--align-right spirit-hero-split-screen__image-container--mobile-top">
			        <img src="/images/home/one-walk.png" class="spirit-hero-split-screen__image spirit-hero-split-screen__image" alt="https://stagingjdrf.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/long-sleeve-tee.jpg">
