                <div class="spirit-hero-split-screen__message spirit-hero-message">
                    <h2 class="spirit-hero-message__title spirit-h2">Approachable</h2>
                    <div class="spirit-long-form-text">
                        <p>We use simple shapes with rounded corners to help our designs feel familiar and approachable. White space, bold typography and strong hierarchy creates balance and structure on the screen without the need for lots of lines, borders and shading.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <figure class="spirit-hero-split-screen__image-container spirit-hero-split-screen__image-container--align-left spirit-hero-split-screen__image-container--mobile-top">
			        <img src="/images/home/one-walk.png" class="spirit-hero-split-screen__image spirit-hero-split-screen__image" alt="https://stagingjdrf.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/long-sleeve-tee.jpg">
