                    <h2 class="spirit-hero-message__title spirit-h2">Striking</h2>
                    <div class="spirit-long-form-text">
                        <p>Brush strokes represent the human spirit of the people that drive our mission forward. They provide warmth to our striking, minimal aesthetic that is at risk of feeling clinical and unapproachable.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <figure class="spirit-hero-split-screen__image-container spirit-hero-split-screen__image-container--align-right spirit-hero-split-screen__image-container--mobile-top">
